121
00:08:36,197 --> 00:08:38,816
Bagus, melaju dengan kecepatan penuh!

122
00:08:38,907 --> 00:08:41,802
Tetap ikuti dia!

123
00:08:45,501 --> 00:08:46,922
Target kita menjauh!

124
00:08:47,012 --> 00:08:48,393
