Cepat! Jika tidak, kita akan kehilangan dia!

130
00:09:06,104 --> 00:09:07,220
Sedang kuusahakan!

131
00:09:07,311 --> 00:09:09,920
Kita juga akan masuk!

132
00:09:15,509 --> 00:09:18,026
Astaga!

133
00:09:18,804 --> 00:09:25,320
Kanan! Kiri! Kanan! Kiri!

134
00:09:25,411 --> 00:09:28,213
- Sekarang jalan lurus!
- Diam! Kau mengganggu konsentrasiku!

135
00:09:33,804 --> 00:09:34,088
(Keadilan)

136
00:09:35,026 --> 00:09:36,816
Kami sudah menunggumu, Topi Jerami!

137
00:09:37,109 --> 00:09:38,736
Semua kapal, tembak!

138
00:09:43,903 --> 00:09:44,994
Bajingan!

139
00:09:46,003 --> 00:09:47,409
Cien Fleurs!

140
00:09:52,709 --> 00:09:54,616
Terima ini!

141
00:09:54,707 --> 00:09:57,916
Bom Asap Pembunuh Super!

142
00:10:01,289 --> 00:10:02,900
Baiklah!

143
00:10:04,293 --> 00:10:06,428
Mari manfaatkan kesempatannya sekarang!

144
00:10:09,399 --> 00:10:10,614
Semua kapal, kepung mereka!

145
00:10:10,705 --> 00:10:12,711
Aktifkan baling-baling!

146
00:10:14,589 --> 00:10:16,614
Kita harus meningkatkan kecepatan!

147
00:10:25,418 --> 00:10:27,117
Astaga, mereka mengejar kita!

148
00:10:27,208 --> 00:10:29,404
Aku tidak bisa menaikkan kecepatan
lebih dari ini!

149
00:10:29,810 --> 00:10:31,311
Sial!

150
00:10:31,401 --> 00:10:33,226
Topiku!

151
00:10:33,618 --> 00:10:34,909
Kau mau ke mana?

152
00:10:42,325 --> 00:10:47,114
Kembalikan topiku!

153
00:10:50,402 --> 00:10:53,509
Gomu Gomu no...

154
00:10:54,718 --> 00:10:58,304
Bazooka!

155
00:11:03,021 --> 00:11:04,021
Tunggu!

156
00:11:09,396 --> 00:11:10,929
Itu topi jeraminya!

157
00:11:23,691 --> 00:11:25,215
Sial!

158
00:11:35,831 --> 00:11:38,120
Semua kapal, berhenti menembak!

159
00:11:38,211 --> 00:11:40,993
Perhatian! Hentikan bomnya!

160
